@page "/aboutus"
<PageTitle>About Us</PageTitle>
<h1 class="text-center"><strong>About Us</strong></h1>

<section class="team-section">
    <div class="team-card">
        <p>Oversees all marketing campaigns and strategies to increase brand awareness and drive adoption.</p>
        <p><strong>John</strong></p>
        <p>Marketing Manager</p>
    </div>
    <div class="team-card">
        <p>Manages the adoption process, conducts intake interviews, and matches potential adopters with suitable pets.</p>
        <p><strong>Fitri</strong></p>
        <p>Adoption Coordinator</p>
    </div>
    <div class="team-card">
        <p>Recruits, trains, and schedules volunteers to assist with various shelter tasks, such as animal care, fundraising, and outreach.</p>
        <p><strong>Sam</strong></p>
        <p>Volunteer Coordinator</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-section-overlay"></div> <!-- The dimming overlay -->
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h2><strong>Our Story</strong></h2>
        <p>
            "We are a passionate group of animal lovers dedicated to finding loving homes for rescued pets.
            We believe that every animal deserves a chance at a happy and fulfilling life,
            and we work tirelessly to connect deserving animals with compassionate families.
            Our mission is to promote responsible pet ownership and to reduce the number of homeless animals in our community.
            We strive to provide a safe and nurturing environment for our adoptable animals and to offer support
            and guidance to prospective adopters throughout the adoption process.
            We are grateful for the opportunity to make a difference in the lives of animals in need
            and to help create lasting bonds between pets and their human companions."
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <div class="footer-columns">
        <div>
            <p><strong>Subscribe</strong></p>
            <form>
                <input type="email" placeholder="Your email" />
                <button type="submit">Subscribe</button>
            </form>
            <p>By subscribing, you agree to receive emails from us and acknowledge our Privacy Policy.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Pet Adoption Center. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#">Terms of Service</a></p>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    body {
        background-color: #FFF5F5; /* Snow background */
        color: #3A5253; /* Dark Slate Gray text */
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    h1 {
        color: #35455D; /* Navy blue */
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .team-section {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        padding: 40px 0;
        background-color: #FFF5F5; /* Snow */
    }

    .team-card {
        background-color: #92B1B6; /* Muted teal */
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        width: 30%;
        text-align: center;
        color: #FFF5F5; /* White text */
    }

    .hero-section {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 40px;
        background-color: #35455D; /* Navy blue */
        background-image: url('Image/ourStory.jpg');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
    }

    .hero-section-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        text-align: center;
        color: #FFF5F5; /* White text */
        max-width: 800px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

        .hero-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

    .footer-columns {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 40px;
        background-color: #35455D; /* Navy blue footer */
        color: #FFF5F5;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
        background-color: #92B1B6; /* Muted teal */
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #FFF5F5;
    }

        .footer-bottom a {
            color: #FFF5F5;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

            .footer-bottom a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }

    button {
        background-color: #E07A5F; /* Burnt sienna */
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #3A5253; /* Dark Slate Gray */
        }

    input[type="email"] {
        padding: 10px;
        width: calc(100% - 20px);
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        border: 1px solid #E07A5F; /* Burnt sienna */
        border-radius: 5px;
    }
</style>

